{%- comment -%}
  LE FIGUE — Custom & Bespoke (/pages/custom-bespoke), v2 design 2026-07-07
  from ~/Downloads/[New] le-figue-custom.html. Theme header/footer wrap it
  (design topbar logo/topnote + footer stripped; its Atelier/Design-Profile
  tab slider KEPT in a non-sticky .lfb-tabbar). CSS scoped .lf-bespoke
  (comments stripped pre-scoping), ids lfb-*, JS root-scoped w/ the
  sticky-progress ancestor-overflow rescue.
  NOTE: booking calendar + survey remain a FRONT-END PROTOTYPE (no real
  submission) — Sesami wiring for the Custom & Bespoke service is a separate
  pending task, same as before this redesign.
{%- endcomment -%}

<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;0,600;1,400;1,500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<link rel="stylesheet" as="style" crossorigin href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/orioncactus/pretendard@v1.3.9/dist/web/variable/pretendardvariable-dynamic-subset.css">

<div class="lf-bespoke">
  <div class="lfb-tabbar">
    <div class="tabs ptabs">
      <button class="active" data-view="lfb-viewAtelier">The Atelier</button>
      <button data-view="lfb-viewProfile">Design Profile</button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ATELIER -->
  <section class="view active" id="lfb-viewAtelier">
    <div class="wrap">

      <section class="c-hero">
        <div class="ct">
          <span class="eyebrow">Custom &amp; Bespoke</span>
          <h1 class="display">Made for you,<br>and you alone.</h1>
          <p>At our NYC atelier, every custom piece begins with a conversation. We take the time to understand your story, your lifestyle, and your vision, then bring it to life with thoughtful craftsmanship.</p>
          <p>From a one of a kind engagement ring to a cherished heirloom reimagined, your piece is designed step by step, from first sketch to final setting, with June by your side throughout.</p>
          <button class="cstart" data-go="lfb-viewProfile">Begin your design profile</button>
        </div>
        <div class="cimg"><span class="ph">Bespoke piece</span></div>
      </section>

      <!-- two paths: Bespoke vs Custom -->
      <div class="stage" style="border-top:1px solid var(--line);padding-top:38px;">
        <div class="stage-head"><span class="stage-tag">Two ways to begin</span><h3 class="display">Bespoke, or fully custom</h3></div>
        <p class="stage-sub">Both are designed with you and made by hand. The difference is simply where we start.</p>
        <div class="paths">
          <div class="path">
            <div class="pe">Bespoke</div>
            <h3>Begin from a LE FIGUE design</h3>
            <p>Take one of our signature settings and make it yours. Adjust the centre stone, metal, and details to your taste and budget, with meaningful touches like engraving.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="path">
            <div class="pe">Custom</div>
            <h3>Begin from a blank page</h3>
            <p>Work directly with June to design a one of a kind piece from your inspirations and your story. From first sketch to final setting, made entirely for you.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- services -->
      <div class="stage">
        <div class="secline">What we make together.</div>
        <div class="svc-grid">
          <div class="svc"><div class="simg"><span class="ph">Engagement rings</span></div>
            <h3>Engagement Rings</h3>
            <p>A stand out classic or an alternative style, set with natural or lab diamonds and gemstones, finished fresh off the bench.</p></div>
          <div class="svc"><div class="simg"><span class="ph">In-store exclusives</span></div>
            <h3>In-Store Exclusives</h3>
            <p>One of one styles housed at 19 Bleecker, often claimed before they reach the webstore. A visit is the way to find them first.</p></div>
          <div class="svc"><div class="simg"><span class="ph">Customs &amp; heirloom</span></div>
            <h3>Customs &amp; Heirloom</h3>
            <p>A piece designed and made just for you, from initial sketch to sourcing stones, or reimagining a treasured heirloom anew.</p></div>
          <div class="svc"><div class="simg"><span class="ph">Wedding &amp; bands</span></div>
            <h3>Wedding &amp; Anniversary</h3>
            <p>Bands and anniversary pieces made with the same care as the day they mark. Quiet symbols, worn for a lifetime.</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- designer -->
      <div class="stage" style="padding:46px 0;">
        <div class="designer">
          <div class="dimg"><span class="ph">June · Designer</span></div>
          <div class="dtxt">
            <span class="sect-eye">Meet the Designer</span>
            <h2 class="display">June</h2>
            <div class="drole">Custom &amp; Bespoke Designer, LE FIGUE</div>
            <p>Every custom piece at LE FIGUE is designed with intention, craftsmanship, and timeless elegance. Inspired by New York, architecture, and the artistry of fine jewelry, each creation is developed from concept to completion, every gemstone and setting carefully considered to feel deeply personal.</p>
            <p>Having majored in Jewelry Design at <b>FIT</b> in New York and currently completing the Diamonds program at <b>GIA</b>, June guides you through stones and settings with the eye of a specialist and the philosophy of proportion, restraint, and meaningful storytelling.</p>
            <p>Over the years she has collaborated with leading brands across Vietnam, Korea, China, and New York, managing both production and design, shaping how she brings each piece to life.</p>
            <div class="dcreds">
              <span class="dcred">FIT · Jewelry Design</span>
              <span class="dcred">GIA · Diamonds</span>
              <span class="dcred">NYC Atelier</span>
            </div>
            <div class="dquote">We don't simply create jewelry. We create pieces that become part of your story.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- process with timeline -->
      <div class="stage">
        <div class="stage-head"><span class="stage-tag">The Art of Bespoke</span><h3 class="display">The journey of creation</h3></div>
        <p class="stage-sub">A bespoke creation is more than fine jewelry. It is a story, thoughtfully designed and made by hand, guided by June from the first conversation to the piece in your hands.</p>
        <div class="process">
          <div class="pstep2"><div class="pn">i</div><h4>Consultation</h4><p>Every piece begins with your story. A proposal, a wedding, an heirloom reimagined, or an idea entirely your own. We listen first, in person or virtually.</p></div>
          <div class="pstep2"><div class="pn">ii</div><h4>Creative Direction</h4><p>We shape the design direction together, with materials, stones, an estimated timeline, and investment. Nothing is made yet.</p></div>
          <div class="pstep2"><div class="pn">iii</div><h4>Project Confirmation</h4><p>Once the direction and estimate feel right, your project is confirmed and our creative journey begins.</p></div>
          <div class="pstep2"><div class="pn">iv</div><h4>Stone Curation</h4><p>GIA graded diamonds and trusted colored gemstones, selected for color, cut, carat, clarity, rarity, and harmony with your design.</p></div>
          <div class="pstep2"><div class="pn">v</div><h4>Design Development</h4><p>Your idea takes shape through hand sketches, design concepts, CAD previews, and photorealistic renderings, compared side by side.</p></div>
          <div class="pstep2"><div class="pn">vi</div><h4>Design Review</h4><p>Proportion, thickness, comfort, stone size, and setting, refined with your feedback until the final design is approved.</p></div>
          <div class="pstep2"><div class="pn">vii</div><h4>Precision Engineering</h4><p>Your approved design is engineered in precise 3D CAD. Every dimension and setting is checked once more before production begins.</p></div>
          <div class="pstep2"><div class="pn">viii</div><h4>Handcrafted Creation</h4><p>Made in New York by skilled artisans, through wax modeling, mold making, precious metal casting, polishing, and hand finishing.</p></div>
          <div class="pstep2"><div class="pn">ix</div><h4>Setting &amp; Inspection</h4><p>Each stone is set by hand, then inspected against our standards for stone security, finish, polish, balance, comfort, and overall craftsmanship.</p></div>
          <div class="pstep2"><div class="pn">x</div><h4>Presentation</h4><p>Your finished piece arrives in our signature packaging, with lifetime cleaning and care to keep it as beautiful as the day you receive it.</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline">
          <span class="tl"><b>8–10 wks</b> stones finalised before your date</span>
          <span class="tl"><b>4–6 wks</b> handcrafting once approved</span>
          <span class="tl"><b>Made in New York</b> at our atelier</span>
          <span class="tl"><b>In person or virtual</b> from anywhere</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- the le figue difference -->
      <div class="stage">
        <div class="stage-head"><span class="stage-tag">The Le Figue Difference</span><h3 class="display">Every detail, considered</h3></div>
        <div class="reassure">
          <div><div class="rt">Guided by a specialist</div><div class="rd">A personal design consultation with June, GIA trained, from first idea to final setting.</div></div>
          <div><div class="rt">GIA standard stones</div><div class="rd">GIA graded diamonds and carefully sourced colored gemstones, natural, lab grown, or rare one of a kind.</div></div>
          <div><div class="rt">Made in New York</div><div class="rd">Handcrafted by skilled artisans at our atelier, from wax model to hand finishing.</div></div>
          <div><div class="rt">Seen before it is made</div><div class="rd">Hand sketches, CAD previews, and photorealistic renderings, so you meet your piece before a single stone is set.</div></div>
          <div><div class="rt">Transparent from the start</div><div class="rd">A clear timeline and investment, agreed together before making begins.</div></div>
          <div><div class="rt">Yours for a lifetime</div><div class="rd">Signature packaging with engraved name and message service, and lifetime cleaning and care.</div></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="atelier-cta">
        <h2 class="display">Your story begins here.</h2>
        <p>Share a little about your vision through our design profile. June reviews each one personally before your consultation.</p>
        <button class="cstart" data-go="lfb-viewProfile">Begin your design profile</button>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- DESIGN PROFILE (all sections visible) -->
  <section class="view" id="lfb-viewProfile">

    <!-- ===== STEP 0 — CHOOSE YOUR HOUR (calendar) ===== -->
    <div class="narrow">
      <div class="survey-intro">
        <span class="eyebrow">The Atelier · By appointment</span>
        <h1 class="display">Choose your hour.</h1>
        <p>Begin by holding a time to meet June, in person at our Bleecker atelier or virtually from anywhere. Then tell us your story below, and we will reserve the two together.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bk-wrap" id="lfb-s0">
      <div class="bk-stage-eye">First</div>
      <div class="bk-stage-title display">Where shall we meet</div>
      <div class="bk-modes" id="lfb-bkModes">
        <button type="button" class="bk-mode on" data-mode="atelier">
          <span class="tick"></span>
          <div class="me">In person</div>
          <div class="mt">The Bleecker Atelier</div>
          <div class="md">19 Bleecker Street, NoHo. The back room is yours for the hour, stones and references on the table.</div>
        </button>
        <button type="button" class="bk-mode" data-mode="virtual">
          <span class="tick"></span>
          <div class="me">From anywhere</div>
          <div class="mt">Virtual Atelier</div>
          <div class="md">A private video call. We send a link once your hour is confirmed, references shared on screen.</div>
        </button>
      </div>

      <div class="bk-stage-eye">Then</div>
      <div class="bk-stage-title display">Find a date that suits you</div>
      <div class="bk-picker">
        <div class="bk-cal">
          <div class="bk-cal-top">
            <div class="bk-cal-month" id="lfb-bkCalMonth">Month<small id="lfb-bkCalYear">Year</small></div>
            <div class="bk-cal-nav">
              <button type="button" id="lfb-bkPrevM" aria-label="Previous month">&#8249;</button>
              <button type="button" id="lfb-bkNextM" aria-label="Next month">&#8250;</button>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="bk-cal-dow"><span>Sun</span><span>Mon</span><span>Tue</span><span>Wed</span><span>Thu</span><span>Fri</span><span>Sat</span></div>
          <div class="bk-cal-grid" id="lfb-bkCalGrid"></div>
          <div class="bk-cal-foot">
            <span class="lg"><span class="dot"></span> Today</span>
            <span class="lg"><span class="sq"></span> Selected</span>
            <span class="lg" style="margin-left:auto;font-style:italic;font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:12px;">Sundays we rest</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bk-timepanel" id="lfb-bkTimePanel">
          <div class="bk-time-empty" id="lfb-bkTimeEmpty">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/><path d="M12 7v5l3 2"/></svg>
            Select a date and we will<br>show you the hours we have open.
          </div>
          <div id="lfb-bkTimeBody" style="display:none;">
            <div class="bk-time-head" id="lfb-bkTimeHead">Available hours</div>
            <div class="bk-time-sub" id="lfb-bkTimeSub">Each session runs about ninety minutes</div>
            <div class="bk-slots" id="lfb-bkSlots"></div>
            <div class="bk-tz" id="lfb-bkTzNote">Times shown in New York (ET)</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bk-summary">
      <div style="flex:1;min-width:240px;">
        <div class="bk-sum-eye">Your hour</div>
        <div class="bk-sum-line" id="lfb-bkSumLine"><span class="muted">Choose a date and time above</span></div>
        <div class="bk-sum-meta" id="lfb-bkSumMeta">The Bleecker Atelier · 19 Bleecker Street, NoHo</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bk-divider"></div>

    <!-- ===== STORY ===== -->
    <div class="narrow">
      <div class="survey-intro">
        <span class="eyebrow">Client Design Profile</span>
        <h1 class="display">Tell us your story.</h1>
        <p>Every custom piece begins with a conversation. The more you share, the more personal your piece becomes. Only your contact details are required, everything else is yours to share as you wish.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- sticky progress (scroll-spy) -->
    <div class="progress" id="lfb-progress">
      <div class="pnode current" data-go-step="lfb-s0"><div class="pdot">&#9733;</div><div class="plabel">Your hour</div></div>
      <div class="pbar"></div>
      <div class="pnode" data-go-step="lfb-s1"><div class="pdot">1</div><div class="plabel">You</div></div>
      <div class="pbar"></div>
      <div class="pnode" data-go-step="lfb-s2"><div class="pdot">2</div><div class="plabel">Occasion</div></div>
      <div class="pbar"></div>
      <div class="pnode" data-go-step="lfb-s3"><div class="pdot">3</div><div class="plabel">Design</div></div>
      <div class="pbar"></div>
      <div class="pnode" data-go-step="lfb-s4"><div class="pdot">4</div><div class="plabel">The Story</div></div>
      <div class="pbar"></div>
      <div class="pnode" data-go-step="lfb-s5"><div class="pdot">5</div><div class="plabel">Lifestyle</div></div>
    </div>

    <form class="narrow" id="lfb-customForm" autocomplete="off">

      <!-- STEP 1 -->
      <div class="step" id="lfb-s1">
        <div class="step-head"><div class="stepn">One</div><h2 class="display">A little about you</h2><div class="sline">So we can reach you, and prepare.</div></div>
        <div class="q"><div class="field"><label>Full name <span style="color:var(--accent);">*</span></label><input type="text" id="lfb-fName" required placeholder="First and last name"></div></div>
        <div class="q"><div class="row2">
          <div class="field"><label>Email address <span style="color:var(--accent);">*</span></label><input type="email" id="lfb-fEmail" required placeholder="you@email.com"></div>
          <div class="field"><label>Phone number</label><input type="tel" placeholder="Optional"></div>
        </div></div>
        <div class="q">
          <span class="qlabel">Preferred consultation</span>
          <div class="chips" data-single><button type="button" class="chip on">In person · NYC atelier</button><button type="button" class="chip">Virtual · from anywhere</button></div>
        </div>
        <div class="q">
          <span class="qlabel">Is this a surprise?</span>
          <div class="qhelp">If so, we will be discreet in how and when we reach you.</div>
          <div class="chips" data-single><button type="button" class="chip">Yes, please be discreet</button><button type="button" class="chip">No, both of us know</button></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- STEP 2 -->
      <div class="step" id="lfb-s2">
        <div class="step-head"><div class="stepn">Two</div><h2 class="display">The occasion</h2><div class="sline">What brings you to LE FIGUE.</div></div>
        <div class="q">
          <span class="qlabel"><span class="qn">1</span>What brings you to LE FIGUE?</span>
          <div class="chips" data-multi>
            <button type="button" class="chip">Proposal</button><button type="button" class="chip">Engagement</button><button type="button" class="chip">Wedding</button>
            <button type="button" class="chip">Anniversary</button><button type="button" class="chip">Birthday</button><button type="button" class="chip">Family heirloom</button>
            <button type="button" class="chip">Celebration</button><button type="button" class="chip">Self gift</button><button type="button" class="chip">Other</button>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="q"><div class="row2">
          <div class="field"><label>A special date to keep in mind?</label><input type="text" placeholder="DD / MM / YYYY"></div>
          <div class="field"><label>Completed by when?</label><input type="text" placeholder="A date you are working toward"></div>
        </div></div>
        <div class="q">
          <span class="qlabel"><span class="qn">2</span>What investment range are you comfortable with?</span>
          <div class="qhelp">Our custom creations begin at $5,000.</div>
          <div class="chips" data-single>
            <button type="button" class="chip">$5,000 – $10,000</button><button type="button" class="chip">$10,000 – $20,000</button><button type="button" class="chip">$20,000 – $30,000</button>
            <button type="button" class="chip">$30,000 – $40,000</button><button type="button" class="chip">$40,000+</button>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="q">
          <span class="qlabel"><span class="qn">3</span>A completely new piece, or redesigning an existing one?</span>
          <div class="chips" data-single><button type="button" class="chip">New design</button><button type="button" class="chip">Redesign</button><button type="button" class="chip">Unsure</button></div>
        </div>
        <div class="q"><span class="qlabel"><span class="qn">4</span>A family heirloom or sentimental piece to redesign or incorporate?</span><div class="field"><textarea rows="2" placeholder="Tell us about it, if so, including any stones you would like us to use"></textarea></div></div>
      </div>

      <!-- STEP 3 — DESIGN (new research-informed section) -->
      <div class="step" id="lfb-s3">
        <div class="step-head"><div class="stepn">Three</div><h2 class="display">The design</h2><div class="sline">Stones, metal, and the details that make it yours.</div></div>
        <div class="q">
          <span class="qlabel"><span class="qn">5</span>Are you drawn to a particular centre stone?</span>
          <div class="chips" data-multi>
            <button type="button" class="chip">Round</button><button type="button" class="chip">Oval</button><button type="button" class="chip">Emerald</button>
            <button type="button" class="chip">Cushion</button><button type="button" class="chip">Pear</button><button type="button" class="chip">Marquise</button>
            <button type="button" class="chip">Radiant</button><button type="button" class="chip">Open to guidance</button>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="q">
          <span class="qlabel"><span class="qn">6</span>Stone preference?</span>
          <div class="chips" data-single>
            <button type="button" class="chip">Natural diamond</button><button type="button" class="chip">Lab grown diamond</button><button type="button" class="chip">Coloured gemstone</button>
            <button type="button" class="chip">A rare one of a kind stone</button><button type="button" class="chip">Unsure, guide me</button>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="q">
          <span class="qlabel"><span class="qn">7</span>Which metal feels like you?</span>
          <div class="chips" data-multi>
            <button type="button" class="chip">Platinum</button><button type="button" class="chip">White gold</button><button type="button" class="chip">Yellow gold</button>
            <button type="button" class="chip">Rose gold</button><button type="button" class="chip">Mixed metals</button><button type="button" class="chip">Unsure</button>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="q"><div class="row2">
          <div class="field"><label>Ring size <span class="opt" style="color:var(--ink-soft);">· if known</span></label><input type="text" placeholder="US size, or we can guide you"></div>
          <div class="field"><label>Engraving or hidden detail?</label><input type="text" placeholder="A date, initials, a private symbol"></div>
        </div></div>
        <div class="q">
          <span class="qlabel"><span class="qn">8</span>Inspiration or reference images</span>
          <div class="qhelp">Photos of your own pieces, references, sketches, or anything that captures the feeling. JPG, PNG, HEIC, or PDF.</div>
          <div class="drop" id="lfb-drop">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 16V4"/><path d="M7 9l5-5 5 5"/><path d="M4 16v3a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h14a1 1 0 0 0 1-1v-3"/></svg>
            <div class="dt">Drag images here, or <span class="browse">browse</span></div>
            <div class="ds">Up to 8 files</div>
            <input type="file" id="lfb-fileInput" accept="image/*,.pdf,.heic" multiple hidden>
          </div>
          <div class="thumbs" id="lfb-thumbs"></div>
          <div class="field" style="margin-top:14px;"><label>Or paste a link <span class="opt" style="color:var(--ink-soft);">· Pinterest, Drive, or a website</span></label><input type="text" placeholder="https://"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="q">
          <span class="qlabel"><span class="qn">9</span>A jewelry house, designer, or style that inspires you?</span>
          <div class="chips" data-multi>
            <button type="button" class="chip">Harry Winston</button><button type="button" class="chip">Cartier</button><button type="button" class="chip">Tiffany &amp; Co.</button>
            <button type="button" class="chip">Van Cleef &amp; Arpels</button><button type="button" class="chip">Graff</button><button type="button" class="chip">Boucheron</button>
            <button type="button" class="chip">Vintage</button><button type="button" class="chip">Minimal</button><button type="button" class="chip">Modern</button><button type="button" class="chip">Architectural</button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- STEP 4 -->
      <div class="step" id="lfb-s4">
        <div class="step-head"><div class="stepn">Four</div><h2 class="display">The story</h2><div class="sline">The most meaningful jewelry tells one.</div></div>
        <div class="poetic">The most meaningful jewelry tells a story.</div>
        <div class="q"><span class="qlabel"><span class="qn">10</span>A special memory, place, person, or life moment this piece should represent?</span><div class="field"><textarea rows="3" placeholder="In your own words"></textarea></div></div>
        <div class="q"><span class="qlabel"><span class="qn">11</span>How would you like this piece to make you feel each time you wear it?</span><div class="field"><textarea rows="2" placeholder=""></textarea></div></div>
        <div class="q"><span class="qlabel"><span class="qn">12</span>If this becomes a future heirloom, what story would you want it to tell?</span><div class="field"><textarea rows="2" placeholder=""></textarea></div></div>
      </div>

      <!-- STEP 5 -->
      <div class="step" id="lfb-s5">
        <div class="step-head"><div class="stepn">Five</div><h2 class="display">Your lifestyle</h2><div class="sline">How this piece will live with you.</div></div>
        <div class="q">
          <span class="qlabel"><span class="qn">13</span>How often do you plan to wear this piece?</span>
          <div class="chips" data-single><button type="button" class="chip">Every day</button><button type="button" class="chip">A few times a week</button><button type="button" class="chip">Special occasions</button><button type="button" class="chip">Unsure</button></div>
        </div>
        <div class="q">
          <span class="qlabel"><span class="qn">14</span>Which words best describe your style?</span>
          <div class="chips" data-multi>
            <button type="button" class="chip">Timeless</button><button type="button" class="chip">Classic</button><button type="button" class="chip">Minimal</button><button type="button" class="chip">Modern</button>
            <button type="button" class="chip">Bold</button><button type="button" class="chip">Vintage</button><button type="button" class="chip">Feminine</button><button type="button" class="chip">Sculptural</button>
            <button type="button" class="chip">Architectural</button><button type="button" class="chip">Organic</button><button type="button" class="chip">Other</button>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="q"><span class="qlabel"><span class="qn">15</span>Anything else you would like us to know before your consultation?</span><div class="field"><textarea rows="3" placeholder=""></textarea></div></div>
      </div>

      <div class="submit-area">
        <div class="held empty" id="lfb-heldReadout">Choose your hour above to reserve your consultation.</div>
        <button type="submit" class="submit">Reserve my consultation</button>
        <div class="snote">Your hour and your profile go to June together. After reviewing your story personally, she will confirm the consultation and begin the conversation.</div>
      </div>
    </form>
  </section>

  <!-- CONFIRMATION -->
  <div class="scrim" id="lfb-scrim"><div class="confirm">
    <div class="seal">&#10003;</div>
    <h3 class="display" id="lfb-confirmTitle">Thank you. Your hour is held and your story is with June.</h3>
    <p class="sub">We look forward to meeting you.</p>
    <div class="resv">
      <div class="rr" id="lfb-rNameRow" style="display:none;"><span class="k">For</span><span class="v" id="lfb-rName">&mdash;</span></div>
      <div class="rr"><span class="k">When</span><span class="v" id="lfb-rWhen">&mdash;</span></div>
      <div class="rr"><span class="k">Time</span><span class="v" id="lfb-rTime">&mdash;</span></div>
      <div class="rr"><span class="k">Where</span><span class="v" id="lfb-rWhere">&mdash;</span></div>
      <div class="rr"><span class="k">With</span><span class="v">June, our designer</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="expect"><b>What happens next.</b> June reviews every profile personally. She will reach out to confirm this hour, and arrive having read your story, first ideas in hand. From stone to sketch to rendering to setting, your custom journey unfolds.</div>
    <button class="cbtn" id="lfb-closeConfirm">Return to The Atelier</button>
  </div></div>
</div>

{% stylesheet %}
  .lf-bespoke{
    --ink:#2a2622;--ink-soft:#6b635a;--line:#e3dccf;--line-soft:#efe9dd;
    --cream:#faf7f1;--cream-deep:#f3ede1;--accent:#8a7250;--gold:#b8975f;--paper:#fdfbf6;
  }
  .lf-bespoke *{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;}
  .lf-bespoke{scroll-behavior:smooth;}
  .lf-bespoke{background:var(--cream);color:var(--ink);
    font-family:'Pretendard Variable','Pretendard',-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',sans-serif;
    font-weight:400;line-height:1.7;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;}
  .lf-bespoke .display{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;}
  .lf-bespoke a{color:inherit;text-decoration:none;}

  
  .lf-bespoke .topbar{position:sticky;top:0;z-index:50;background:rgba(253,251,246,.97);backdrop-filter:blur(8px);-webkit-backdrop-filter:blur(8px);border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);}
  .lf-bespoke .topbar-in{max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 28px;height:70px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:18px;}
  .lf-bespoke .logo{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-weight:600;font-size:22px;letter-spacing:.32em;text-transform:uppercase;white-space:nowrap;}
  .lf-bespoke .logo small{display:block;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:.34em;color:var(--ink-soft);font-weight:400;margin-top:2px;}
  .lf-bespoke .tabs{display:flex;gap:6px;background:var(--cream-deep);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:40px;padding:5px;}
  .lf-bespoke .tabs button{background:none;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-style:italic;font-size:14.5px;color:var(--ink-soft);padding:8px 18px;border-radius:30px;transition:.2s;white-space:nowrap;}
  .lf-bespoke .tabs button.active{background:var(--accent);color:#f7f1e6;}
  .lf-bespoke .topnote{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-style:italic;font-size:14px;color:var(--ink-soft);white-space:nowrap;}

  
  .lf-bespoke .wrap{max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 28px;}
  .lf-bespoke .narrow{max-width:760px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 28px;}
  .lf-bespoke .view{display:none;}
  .lf-bespoke .view.active{display:block;}
  .lf-bespoke .eyebrow{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-style:italic;color:var(--accent);font-size:15px;letter-spacing:.02em;}
  .lf-bespoke .sect-eye{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-style:italic;color:var(--gold);font-size:14px;letter-spacing:.04em;}

  
  .lf-bespoke .s-hero{padding:60px 0 8px;text-align:center;max-width:680px;margin:0 auto;}
  .lf-bespoke .s-hero h1{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-weight:500;font-size:clamp(34px,5vw,54px);line-height:1.06;margin:12px 0 16px;}
  .lf-bespoke .s-hero p{font-size:15.5px;color:var(--ink-soft);max-width:540px;margin:0 auto;}

  
  .lf-bespoke .stage{border-top:1px solid var(--line);padding:32px 0;}
  .lf-bespoke .stage:first-of-type{border-top:none;}
  .lf-bespoke .stage-head{display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:12px;margin-bottom:6px;}
  .lf-bespoke .stage-tag{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-style:italic;font-size:14px;color:var(--gold);}
  .lf-bespoke .stage-head h3{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-weight:500;font-size:25px;}
  .lf-bespoke .stage-head .hint{margin-left:auto;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--ink-soft);}
  .lf-bespoke .stage-sub{font-size:13.5px;color:var(--ink-soft);margin-bottom:22px;max-width:560px;}

  
  .lf-bespoke .cases{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:14px;}
  .lf-bespoke .case{border:1px solid var(--line);background:var(--paper);padding:20px 20px 18px;cursor:pointer;transition:.18s;position:relative;text-align:left;display:flex;flex-direction:column;min-height:172px;}
  .lf-bespoke .case:hover{border-color:var(--accent);}
  .lf-bespoke .case.on{border-color:var(--accent);box-shadow:inset 0 0 0 1px var(--accent);background:#fffdf8;}
  .lf-bespoke .case .ce{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-style:italic;color:var(--gold);font-size:13px;}
  .lf-bespoke .case .cn{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:21px;line-height:1.1;margin:3px 0 8px;}
  .lf-bespoke .case .cd{font-size:12.5px;color:var(--ink-soft);line-height:1.55;flex:1;}
  .lf-bespoke .case .cdur{font-size:10.5px;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--accent);margin-top:10px;}
  .lf-bespoke .case .tick{position:absolute;top:16px;right:16px;width:18px;height:18px;border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:50%;transition:.18s;}
  .lf-bespoke .case.on .tick{background:var(--accent);border-color:var(--accent);}
  .lf-bespoke .case.on .tick::after{content:"";position:absolute;left:5px;top:8px;width:4px;height:7px;border:1.6px solid #fff;border-top:none;border-left:none;transform:rotate(40deg);}

  
  .lf-bespoke .seg{display:flex;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap;}
  .lf-bespoke .seg button{flex:1;min-width:180px;border:1px solid var(--line);background:var(--paper);padding:14px 16px;cursor:pointer;text-align:left;transition:.18s;}
  .lf-bespoke .seg button:hover{border-color:var(--accent);}
  .lf-bespoke .seg button.on{border-color:var(--accent);box-shadow:inset 0 0 0 1px var(--accent);background:#fffdf8;}
  .lf-bespoke .seg .t{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:17px;}
  .lf-bespoke .seg .s{font-size:12px;color:var(--ink-soft);margin-top:2px;}

  
  .lf-bespoke .field{margin-bottom:18px;}
  .lf-bespoke .field > label,.lf-bespoke .qlabel{display:block;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--ink-soft);margin-bottom:8px;}
  .lf-bespoke .opt{text-transform:none;letter-spacing:0;color:#bcae93;font-style:normal;}
  .lf-bespoke .helptext{font-size:12px;color:var(--ink-soft);margin:-2px 0 9px;line-height:1.5;}
  
  .lf-bespoke .ear-fig{display:flex;justify-content:center;margin:4px 0 14px;}
  .lf-bespoke .ear-fig svg{width:100%;max-width:260px;height:auto;font-family:'Pretendard Variable',sans-serif;}
  .lf-bespoke .ear-num text{font-size:11px;font-weight:600;fill:#fff;text-anchor:middle;pointer-events:none;}
  .lf-bespoke .ear-pt{cursor:pointer;}
  .lf-bespoke .ear-pt circle{fill:#a4906c;transition:.16s;}
  .lf-bespoke .ear-pt:hover circle{fill:#8a7250;}
  .lf-bespoke .ear-pt.on circle{fill:#b8975f;stroke:#2a2622;stroke-width:1.6;}
  .lf-bespoke .chips.s-ear{display:block;}
  .lf-bespoke .s-ear .earzone{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-style:italic;color:var(--gold);font-size:12.5px;margin:14px 0 8px;}
  .lf-bespoke .s-ear .earzone:first-child{margin-top:2px;}
  .lf-bespoke .s-ear .chiprow{display:flex;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap;}
  .lf-bespoke .chip .cnum{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;width:16px;height:16px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--cream-deep);color:var(--accent);font-family:'Pretendard Variable',sans-serif;font-size:9.5px;font-weight:600;margin-right:7px;vertical-align:middle;}
  .lf-bespoke .chip.on .cnum{background:rgba(255,255,255,.28);color:#fff;}
  .lf-bespoke .field input,.lf-bespoke .field textarea{width:100%;border:1px solid var(--line);background:var(--paper);padding:11px 13px;font-family:'Pretendard Variable',sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:var(--ink);outline:none;transition:.18s;}
  .lf-bespoke .field input:focus,.lf-bespoke .field textarea:focus{border-color:var(--accent);}
  .lf-bespoke .row2{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:12px;}
  .lf-bespoke .row3{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr;gap:12px;}
  .lf-bespoke .chips{display:flex;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap;}
  .lf-bespoke .chip{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:14px;padding:8px 15px;border:1px solid var(--line);background:var(--paper);color:var(--ink-soft);cursor:pointer;border-radius:30px;transition:.16s;}
  .lf-bespoke .chip:hover{border-color:var(--accent);color:var(--ink);}
  .lf-bespoke .chip.on{background:var(--accent);color:#f7f1e6;border-color:var(--accent);}
  .lf-bespoke .consent{display:flex;gap:10px;align-items:flex-start;margin-top:10px;font-size:12.5px;color:var(--ink-soft);}
  .lf-bespoke .consent input{margin-top:3px;accent-color:var(--accent);}
  .lf-bespoke .casepanel{display:none;}
  .lf-bespoke .casepanel.active{display:block;animation:lfb-fade .4s ease both;}
  @keyframes lfb-fade{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(6px)}to{opacity:1;transform:none}}
  @media(prefers-reduced-motion:reduce){.lf-bespoke .casepanel.active{animation:none}}
  .lf-bespoke .panel-banner{border:1px solid var(--line);border-left:2px solid var(--accent);background:var(--paper);padding:12px 16px;font-size:13px;color:var(--ink-soft);margin-bottom:22px;}
  .lf-bespoke .panel-banner b{color:var(--ink);font-weight:500;font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-style:italic;font-size:15px;}

  
  .lf-bespoke .defer{display:flex;gap:12px;align-items:flex-start;border:1px solid var(--line);border-left:2px solid var(--gold);background:var(--paper);padding:14px 16px;margin-bottom:22px;cursor:pointer;transition:.18s;}
  .lf-bespoke .defer:hover{border-color:var(--accent);border-left-color:var(--accent);}
  .lf-bespoke .defer:has(input:checked){border-color:var(--accent);border-left-color:var(--accent);background:#fffdf8;}
  .lf-bespoke .defer input{margin-top:3px;accent-color:var(--accent);flex-shrink:0;}
  .lf-bespoke .defer .dt{font-size:13px;color:var(--ink-soft);line-height:1.6;}
  .lf-bespoke .defer .dt b{display:block;color:var(--ink);font-weight:500;font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-style:italic;font-size:16px;margin-bottom:1px;}
  .lf-bespoke #part2Body[hidden]{display:none;}

  .lf-bespoke .submitbar{border-top:1px solid var(--line);padding:30px 0 8px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:20px;flex-wrap:wrap;}
  .lf-bespoke .submit{background:var(--ink);color:#f4eee2;font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-style:italic;font-size:16px;padding:15px 34px;border:none;cursor:pointer;transition:.2s;}
  .lf-bespoke .submit:hover{background:var(--accent);}
  .lf-bespoke .submit:disabled{background:#cabfa8;cursor:not-allowed;}
  .lf-bespoke .submitnote{font-size:12px;color:var(--ink-soft);max-width:360px;line-height:1.55;}

  
  .lf-bespoke .legend{border-top:1px solid var(--line);border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);background:var(--cream-deep);margin-top:6px;}
  .lf-bespoke .legend-in{max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto;padding:26px 28px;display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:22px;}
  .lf-bespoke .leg .ll{font-size:10.5px;letter-spacing:.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold);margin-bottom:5px;}
  .lf-bespoke .leg .lv{font-size:12.5px;color:var(--ink-soft);line-height:1.5;}

  
  .lf-bespoke .scrim{position:fixed;inset:0;background:rgba(33,29,25,.5);z-index:90;display:none;align-items:flex-start;justify-content:center;padding:40px 20px;overflow-y:auto;}
  .lf-bespoke .scrim.open{display:flex;}
  .lf-bespoke .confirm{background:var(--paper);max-width:500px;width:100%;border:1px solid var(--line);box-shadow:0 40px 80px -30px rgba(0,0,0,.5);padding:38px 34px 30px;}
  .lf-bespoke .confirm .seal{width:46px;height:46px;border:1px solid var(--accent);border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-style:italic;color:var(--accent);font-size:20px;margin-bottom:18px;}
  .lf-bespoke .confirm h3{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-weight:500;font-size:27px;margin-bottom:6px;}
  .lf-bespoke .confirm .sub{font-size:14px;color:var(--ink-soft);margin-bottom:22px;}
  .lf-bespoke .expect{font-size:13px;color:var(--ink-soft);line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:20px;border:1px solid var(--line);background:var(--cream);padding:16px 18px;}
  .lf-bespoke .expect b{color:var(--ink);font-weight:500;}
  .lf-bespoke .cbtn{width:100%;text-align:center;font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-style:italic;font-size:15px;padding:13px;border:1px solid var(--accent);color:#f7f1e6;background:var(--accent);cursor:pointer;transition:.18s;}
  .lf-bespoke .cbtn:hover{background:var(--ink);border-color:var(--ink);}

  
  .lf-bespoke .n-hero{padding:54px 0 10px;max-width:780px;}
  .lf-bespoke .n-hero h1{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-weight:500;font-size:clamp(30px,4.4vw,46px);line-height:1.1;margin:10px 0 14px;}
  .lf-bespoke .n-hero p{font-size:15px;color:var(--ink-soft);max-width:640px;}
  .lf-bespoke .nblock{border-top:1px solid var(--line);padding:30px 0;}
  .lf-bespoke .nblock h2{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-weight:500;font-size:25px;margin-bottom:4px;}
  .lf-bespoke .nblock .nlead{font-size:13.5px;color:var(--ink-soft);margin-bottom:18px;max-width:680px;}
  .lf-bespoke .nblock p{font-size:14px;color:var(--ink-soft);margin-bottom:12px;max-width:760px;}
  .lf-bespoke .nblock strong{color:var(--ink);font-weight:600;}
  .lf-bespoke .ntable{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;margin:6px 0 12px;font-size:13px;}
  .lf-bespoke .ntable th,.lf-bespoke .ntable td{border:1px solid var(--line);padding:10px 12px;text-align:left;vertical-align:top;color:var(--ink-soft);line-height:1.5;}
  .lf-bespoke .ntable th{background:var(--cream-deep);color:var(--ink);font-weight:500;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.06em;text-transform:uppercase;}
  .lf-bespoke .ntable td b{color:var(--ink);font-weight:600;}
  .lf-bespoke .nlist{list-style:none;max-width:760px;}
  .lf-bespoke .nlist li{font-size:13.5px;color:var(--ink-soft);padding:6px 0 6px 20px;position:relative;line-height:1.6;}
  .lf-bespoke .nlist li::before{content:"—";position:absolute;left:0;color:var(--accent);}
  .lf-bespoke .nlist li b{color:var(--ink);font-weight:600;}
  .lf-bespoke .pill{display:inline-block;font-size:10.5px;letter-spacing:.08em;text-transform:uppercase;padding:2px 9px;border-radius:20px;border:1px solid var(--line);color:var(--accent);background:var(--paper);margin-right:4px;}
  .lf-bespoke .pill.req{background:var(--accent);color:#f7f1e6;border-color:var(--accent);}
  .lf-bespoke .src{font-size:11.5px;color:var(--ink-soft);margin-top:4px;}
  .lf-bespoke .src a{border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);}

  .lf-bespoke footer{background:#211d19;color:#8d8474;padding:32px 28px;text-align:center;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.14em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-top:10px;}
  .lf-bespoke footer b{color:#cfc6b6;font-weight:500;}

  
  @media(max-width:880px){
    .lf-bespoke .cases{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
    .lf-bespoke .legend-in{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;}
    .lf-bespoke .topbar-in{flex-direction:column;height:auto;padding:12px 20px;gap:10px;}
    .lf-bespoke .tabs button{font-size:13px;padding:7px 14px;}
  }
  @media(max-width:560px){
    .lf-bespoke .row2,.lf-bespoke .row3{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
    .lf-bespoke .legend-in{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
    .lf-bespoke .ntable{display:block;overflow-x:auto;white-space:nowrap;}
  }


  

  
  .lf-bespoke .ptabs{display:flex;gap:6px;background:var(--cream-deep);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:40px;padding:5px;}
  .lf-bespoke .ptabs button{background:none;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-style:italic;font-size:14.5px;color:var(--ink-soft);padding:8px 20px;border-radius:30px;transition:.2s;white-space:nowrap;}
  .lf-bespoke .ptabs button.active{background:var(--accent);color:#f7f1e6;}

  .lf-bespoke .view{display:none;}
  .lf-bespoke .view.active{display:block;animation:lfb-fade .35s ease both;}
  @keyframes lfb-fade{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(6px)}to{opacity:1;transform:none}}

  
  .lf-bespoke .c-hero{padding:54px 0 36px;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1.05fr .95fr;gap:50px;align-items:center;}
  .lf-bespoke .c-hero .ct .eyebrow{margin-bottom:12px;display:block;}
  .lf-bespoke .c-hero .ct h1{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-weight:500;font-size:clamp(38px,5.4vw,64px);line-height:1.02;letter-spacing:-.015em;margin-bottom:18px;}
  .lf-bespoke .c-hero .ct p{font-size:14.5px;color:var(--ink-soft);line-height:1.85;max-width:470px;margin-bottom:13px;}
  .lf-bespoke .c-hero .cstart{margin-top:24px;display:inline-block;font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-style:italic;font-size:16px;color:#f4eee2;background:var(--ink);padding:13px 30px;cursor:pointer;border:none;transition:.2s;}
  .lf-bespoke .c-hero .cstart:hover{background:var(--accent);}
  .lf-bespoke .c-hero .cimg{aspect-ratio:4/5;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f0e7da,#e3d6c4);overflow:hidden;position:relative;}
  .lf-bespoke .c-hero .cimg .ph{position:absolute;inset:0;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;color:#bda988;font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-style:italic;}
  @media(max-width:880px){.lf-bespoke .c-hero{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:26px;}.lf-bespoke .c-hero .cimg{aspect-ratio:16/10;}}

  .lf-bespoke .secline{text-align:center;font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-style:italic;font-size:clamp(18px,2.3vw,23px);color:var(--accent);padding:8px 20px 26px;}

  .lf-bespoke .svc-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:34px 30px;}
  .lf-bespoke .svc .simg{aspect-ratio:3/2;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f0e7da,#e3d6c4);overflow:hidden;position:relative;margin-bottom:14px;}
  .lf-bespoke .svc .simg .ph{position:absolute;inset:0;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;color:#bda988;font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-style:italic;font-size:13px;}
  .lf-bespoke .svc h3{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-weight:500;font-size:22px;line-height:1.15;margin-bottom:7px;text-align:center;}
  .lf-bespoke .svc p{font-size:13px;color:var(--ink-soft);line-height:1.7;text-align:center;max-width:420px;margin:0 auto;}
